game.name: Princess Hawaii Style
game.description:
Time has come when the two princesses Anna and Rapunzel is ready to go on her most awaited vacation trip in Hawaii! Season is too hot, but the availability of countless malls and shops would help make her dream come true with ease. But the problem is that they both are new to the city and have limited cash to spend. Will you be able to guide her properly? Join Princess Hawaii Style game and be prepared to put your fashion designer skills to test!
Make sure to guide the princesses towards the right mall and purchase a fabulous range of outfits for their holiday in this brand new dressing game. They have chosen you as the entire city call you as a fashionista so your good fashion sense will definitely help them to shop for the right products quickly. First, choose the princess you want to go with shopping and then help her to purchase all the products, including a pair of shoes, tiara, and a matching goggle. 
Once you complete the shopping for the first princess, try to repeat the same for the second one. Now it will be in your hands how to help them to find out a perfect outfit and make their vacation worth remembering forever. Both the princesses trust you, so do not let them feel down and take your time before making a final decision. All the best for dressing them up in Hawaii style!!
